Readme Notes

In order to run nicrosoft_moving_average_crossover_point.py install latest Python.
https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-3144/
Scroll down to Windows Download Pyhton Install Manager.

After successful Python install type pip intall yfinance in cli to install yfinace API.
In cli type pip install mathplotlib
In cli type pip install numpy
In cli type pip install pandas

After the required modules are successfully installed type python microsoft_moving_average_crossover_poiint.py

